<plot>The smallest gesture can mean everything to a lonely soul. 'Mindy' is a beautiful and simple short film about finding someone you can relate with. Mindy, 10, who has no friends at school or at the Chinese restaurant that she helps her mother run, tries to befriend a quiet 11 year old boy who is kind to her one day on the schoolbus.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?370749</url></doc>
